# 📡 8. **BRAND REPOSITORY**

`brand_repository.dart`

```dart
class BrandRepository {
  final Dio dio;

  BrandRepository(this.dio);

  Future<List<Brand>> getBrands() async {
    final res = await dio.get("/brands");
    return (res.data as List).map((e) => Brand.fromJson(e)).toList();
  }
}
```

