# ✅ **6. router/guards/brand_guard.dart**

Jika brand belum dipilih → redirect ke brand selector.

```dart
import '../../../brand/brand_provider.dart';
import '../../router/routes.dart';
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';

String? brandGuard(WidgetRef ref, GoRouterState state) {
  final selectedBrand = ref.read(selectedBrandProvider);

  final isSelectingBrand = state.location == AppRoutes.brandSelector;

  if (selectedBrand == null && !isSelectingBrand) {
    return AppRoutes.brandSelector;
  }

  return null;
}
```

