# 🚀 **5. Logging API Request/Response (Dio Interceptor)**  
Di file:

```
core/network/interceptors/log_interceptor.dart
```

```dart
class APILogInterceptor extends Interceptor {
  @override
  void onRequest(RequestOptions options, RequestInterceptorHandler handler) {
    print("🌐 API REQUEST → ${options.method} ${options.uri}");
    print("Headers: ${options.headers}");
    print("Body: ${options.data}");
    super.onRequest(options, handler);
  }

  @override
  void onResponse(Response response, ResponseInterceptorHandler handler) {
    print("✅ API RESPONSE → ${response.statusCode} ${response.requestOptions.uri}");
    print("Data: ${response.data}");
    super.onResponse(response, handler);
  }

  @override
  void onError(DioException err, ErrorInterceptorHandler handler) {
    print("❌ API ERROR → ${err.requestOptions.uri}");
    print("Message: ${err.message}");
    super.onError(err, handler);
  }
}
```

### Contoh Output:
```
🌐 API REQUEST → GET https://api.sushitei.com/brands
Body: null
✅ API RESPONSE → 200 https://api.sushitei.com/brands
Data: [{ "id": 1, "name": "Sushi Tei", ... }]
```

