# 🔒 6. **Brand Guard Final Version**

```dart
String? brandGuard(WidgetRef ref, GoRouterState state) {
  final brand = ref.read(selectedBrandProvider);

  if (state.location == AppRoutes.splash ||
      state.location == AppRoutes.landing) {
    return null;
  }

  if (brand == null) {
    return AppRoutes.landing;
  }

  return null;
}
```

Guard ini memastikan:

- Tidak bisa masuk dashboard tanpa memilih brand.

