# 🛡️ **6. brand_guard.dart (Flow terbaru)**  
Agar tidak masuk dashboard sebelum pilih brand → wilayah aman.

```dart
String? brandGuard(WidgetRef ref, GoRouterState state) {
  final brand = ref.read(selectedBrandProvider);

  // splash dan landing selalu diizinkan
  if (state.location == AppRoutes.splash ||
      state.location == AppRoutes.landing) {
    return null;
  }

  // brand belum dipilih → redirect ke landing
  if (brand == null) {
    return AppRoutes.landing;
  }

  return null;
}
```

