## 3) Pastikan redirect juga punya guards (combine dengan code di atas)
Contoh `redirect` yang aman:

```dart
redirect: (context, state) {
  final auth = ref.read(authCoreProvider);
  final brand = ref.read(brandProvider);

  final networkAsync = ref.read(networkStatusStreamProvider);
  final bool online = networkAsync.maybeWhen(data: (val) => val, loading: () => true, orElse: () => true);

  final loc = state.location;
  final onLogin = loc == '/login';
  final onNetwork = loc == '/network-loose';

  // if offline, go to network page only if not already there
  if (!online && !onNetwork) {
    ref.read(lastRouteBeforeOfflineProvider.notifier).state = loc;
    if (loc != '/network-loose') return '/network-loose';
    return null;
  }

  // if online and on network page -> return to last or main
  if (online && onNetwork) {
    final last = ref.read(lastRouteBeforeOfflineProvider);
    ref.read(lastRouteBeforeOfflineProvider.notifier).state = null;
    final goTo = (last != null && last != '/network-loose') ? last : '/main';
    if (loc != goTo) return goTo;
    return null;
  }

  // auth logic
  final loggedIn = auth.isLoggedIn;
  if (!loggedIn && !onLogin && loc != '/login') return '/login';
  if (loggedIn && (onLogin || loc == '/')) {
    if (brand != null && loc != '/main') return '/main';
    if (brand == null && loc != '/select-brand') return '/select-brand';
  }

  return null;
}
```

