## 4) `first_loader.dart` — splash / init flow
Contoh `FirstLoader` sebagai route `"/"` — melakukan async inisialisasi lalu navigasi:

```dart
// first_loader.dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';
import 'core/services/brand.s.dart';
import 'core/auth/auth.c.dart';

class FirstLoader extends ConsumerStatefulWidget {
  const FirstLoader({super.key});
  @override
  ConsumerState<FirstLoader> createState() => _FirstLoaderState();
}

class _FirstLoaderState extends ConsumerState<FirstLoader> {
  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _initAll();
  }

  Future<void> _initAll() async {
    try {
      // 1) load stored auth token / session
      await ref.read(authCoreProvider.notifier).restoreSession();

      // 2) load brands (or selected brand)
      final brands = await BrandService().loadBrands(); // contoh synchronous service
      // optionally select default brand if saved
      final defaultBrand = brands.isNotEmpty ? brands.first : null;
      if (defaultBrand != null) {
        ref.read(brandProvider.notifier).state = defaultBrand;
      }

      // 3) after initialization navigate to app main (GoRouter redirect will handle real path)
      // use context.go or router to go to '/main' or root - but prefer to let redirect decide
      // direct navigate to '/' to trigger redirect
      if (mounted) {
        // go to root so AppRouter.redirect can evaluate
        context.go('/');
      }
    } catch (e, st) {
      debugPrint('FirstLoader init error: $e');
      // show error UI or navigate to offline/login accordingly
    }
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return const Scaffold(
      body: Center(
        child: CircularProgressIndicator(),
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

Tambahkan route `'/'` yang menampilkan `FirstLoader` di definisi routes (`authRoutes` atau brandRoutes).

