Bisa banget 🙌  
Dari struktur yang kamu punya, itu malah **sangat memungkinkan** untuk dijadiin **1 dashboard generik** yang dipakai semua brand, terus bedanya di-*drive* lewat **config/brand model**.

---

## 1. Konsep besarnya

Alih-alih:

```text
sushitei.d.ui.dart
hokkaidoya.d.ui.dart
...
```

Kamu bisa punya:

```text
dashboard
  ui
    dashboard.ui.dart      // 1 file untuk semua brand
  widgets
    dashboard.w.dart       // widget2 umum
```

Terus per-brand cukup diwakili oleh:

- `Brand` model (`brand.m.dart`)
- config per brand (warna, logo, menu, dll)
- router yang kirim `brandId` / `Brand` ke dashboard

---

## 2. Contoh model brand

`brand.m.dart`:

```dart
enum BrandType { sushitei, hokkaidoya }

class Brand {
  final BrandType type;
  final String name;
  final String logoAsset;
  final Color primaryColor;
  final List<DashboardMenuItem> menu;

  Brand({
    required this.type,
    required this.name,
    required this.logoAsset,
    required this.primaryColor,
    required this.menu,
  });
}

class DashboardMenuItem {
  final String id;
  final String label;
  final IconData icon;

  DashboardMenuItem({
    required this.id,
    required this.label,
    required this.icon,
  });
}
```

---

## 3. Service untuk brand

`services/brand.s.dart`:

```dart
class BrandService {
  static final _brands = <Brand>[
    Brand(
      type: BrandType.sushitei,
      name: 'Sushi Tei',
      logoAsset: 'assets/brands/sushitei/logo.png',
      primaryColor: Colors.green,
      menu: [
        DashboardMenuItem(id: 'overview', label: 'Overview', icon: Icons.home),
        DashboardMenuItem(id: 'orders', label: 'Orders', icon: Icons.list),
      ],
    ),
    Brand(
      type: BrandType.hokkaidoya,
      name: 'Hokkaidoya',
      logoAsset: 'assets/brands/hokkaidoya/logo.png',
      primaryColor: Colors.red,
      menu: [
        DashboardMenuItem(id: 'overview', label: 'Overview', icon: Icons.home),
        DashboardMenuItem(id: 'reservations', label: 'Reservations', icon: Icons.event),
      ],
    ),
  ];

  Brand getByType(BrandType type) =>
      _brands.firstWhere((b) => b.type == type);
}
```

---

## 4. Satu dashboard untuk semua

`dashboard/ui/dashboard.ui.dart`:

```dart
