## 5. Routing per brand

Daripada punya file UI dashboard per brand, kamu bisa:

`routers/brand_router/brand.r.dart`:

```dart
class BrandRoutes {
  static const dashboard = '/brand/:brandType/dashboard';
}
```

`routers/brand_router/sushitei.r.dart` (opsional, kalau mau alias khusus):

```dart
GoRoute(
  path: '/sushitei/dashboard',
  builder: (context, state) {
    final brand = BrandService().getByType(BrandType.sushitei);
    return BrandDashboardPage(brand: brand);
  },
),
```

`routers/brand_router/hokkaidoya.r.dart` mirip, cuma beda `BrandType`.

Bisa juga lebih generik, route-nya:

```dart
GoRoute(
  path: '/brand/:brandType/dashboard',
  builder: (context, state) {
    final brandTypeStr = state.pathParameters['brandType']!;
    final brandType = BrandType.values.firstWhere(
      (e) => e.name == brandTypeStr,
    );
    final brand = BrandService().getByType(brandType);
    return BrandDashboardPage(brand: brand);
  },
),
```

Jadi bener-bener cuma **1 page**.

