## 1. Pastikan route `SushiTei` diset dengan benar

### `sushitei.r.dart`

```dart
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';
import 'package:stg/screens/brand_sushitei/ui/sushitei_dashboard.ui.dart';

final sushiteiRoute = <GoRoute>[
  GoRoute(
    path: 'sushitei', // ⬅️ TANPA slash di depan karena nested di /brands
    name: 'sushitei',
    builder: (context, state) => const SushiTeiDashboardUI(),
  ),
];
```

> Penting: `path: 'sushitei'` (relative), **bukan** `'/sushitei'`.

