## 2. Parent `/brands` harus punya builder **atau** redirect yang benar

Kamu punya:

```dart
final brandRoutes = <RouteBase>[
  GoRoute(
    path: '/brands',
    name: 'brands',
    routes: [...sushiteiRoute],
  ),
];
```

Ubah jadi salah satu dari dua opsi ini:

### Opsi A — `/brands` punya halaman sendiri

```dart
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';
import 'package:stg/routers/brand_router/sushitei.r.dart';
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

final brandRoutes = <RouteBase>[
  GoRoute(
    path: '/brands',
    name: 'brands',
    builder: (context, state) => const Scaffold(
      body: Center(child: Text('Brands page')), // ganti dengan BrandsUI kamu
    ),
    routes: [
      ...sushiteiRoute,
    ],
  ),
];
```

Lalu kalau mau ke SushiTei:

```dart
context.go('/brands/sushitei');
```

---

### Opsi B — `/brands` cuma redirect ke SushiTei

Kalau kamu **nggak butuh** layar `/brands`, tapi mau langsung masuk ke SushiTei:

```dart
final brandRoutes = <RouteBase>[
  GoRoute(
    path: '/brands',
    name: 'brands',
    redirect: (context, state) {
      // Hindari redirect loop, cek dulu lokasinya
      if (state.matchedLocation == '/brands') {
        return '/brands/sushitei';
      }
      return null;
    },
    routes: [
      ...sushiteiRoute,
    ],
  ),
];
```

Dan di auth redirect:

```dart
// Kalau sudah login tapi masih di /login → pindah ke SushiTei
if (loggedIn && onLoginPage) {
  return '/brands/sushitei'; // ⬅️ ini, bukan cuma '/brands'
}
```

