## 1. Ubah `AppRouter.createRouter` supaya bisa akses `ref`

Sekarang:

```dart
class AppRouter {
  AppRouter._();

  static GoRouter createRouter(AuthCoreNotifier authCoreNotifier) {
    return GoRouter(
      ...
    );
  }
}
```

Ubah jadi (pakai Riverpod `WidgetRef`):

```dart
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import '../providers/brand_provider.dart'; // dimana pun brandProvider didefinisikan

class AppRouter {
  AppRouter._();

  static GoRouter createRouter(WidgetRef ref, AuthCoreNotifier authCoreNotifier) {
    return GoRouter(
      initialLocation: '/',
      debugLogDiagnostics: true,
      refreshListenable: authCoreNotifier,
      redirect: (context, state) {
        final bool loggedIn = authCoreNotifier.isLoggedIn;
        final bool onLoginPage = state.matchedLocation == '/login';
        final bool onRoot = state.matchedLocation == '/';

        // baca brand terpilih dari provider
        final brand = ref.read(brandProvider); // BrandModel?

        // belum login → lempar ke /login
        if (!loggedIn && !onLoginPage) {
          return '/login';
        }

        // sudah login, dan lagi di /login atau di root '/'
        if (loggedIn && (onLoginPage || onRoot)) {
          // kalau brand sudah dipilih → langsung ke dashboard brand
          if (brand != null) {
            // misal BrandModel punya field `code` = 'sushitei'
            final brandPath = '/brands/${brand.code}';
            return brandPath;
          }

          // kalau belum ada brand terpilih → ke halaman pilih brand
          return '/brands';
        }

        // tidak ada redirect
        return null;
      },
      routes: [
        ...authRoutes,
        ...brandRoutes,
      ],
      errorBuilder: (context, state) {
        return Scaffold(
          appBar: AppBar(title: const Text('404')),
          body: Center(child: Text('Halaman tidak ditemukan: ${state.error}')),
        );
      },
    );
  }
}
```

Kunci yang berubah:

```dart
static GoRouter createRouter(WidgetRef ref, AuthCoreNotifier authCoreNotifier)
```

dan di dalam `redirect`:

```dart
final brand = ref.read(brandProvider);
if (brand != null) {
  return '/brands/${brand.code}';
}
```

> Kalau kamu pakai property lain di `BrandModel`, tinggal ganti `${brand.code}` jadi `${brand.slug}` atau langsung simpan full path di model (`brand.routePath`).

