## 2. Panggil `createRouter` dari `App` dengan `ref`

Misal `App` kamu `ConsumerWidget` atau `ConsumerStatefulWidget`, di `build`:

```dart
class App extends ConsumerWidget {
  const App({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context, WidgetRef ref) {
    final authCoreNotifier = ref.watch(authCoreNotifierProvider);
    final router = AppRouter.createRouter(ref, authCoreNotifier);

    return MaterialApp.router(
      routerConfig: router,
      // theme, etc...
    );
  }
}
```

