    builder: (context, state) => SushiTeiDashboardUI(),
  ),
];
```

### 🔧 Fix 1 — Bikin nama route-nya unik

Paling simpel: ubah salah satu `name`-nya.

Misalnya:

```dart
// brand_routes.dart
final brandRoutes = <RouteBase>[
  GoRoute(
    path: '/sushitei',
    name: 'sushitei.root', // ganti nama
    builder: (context, state) => const SushiTeiDashboardUI(),
    routes: [...sushiteiRoute],
  ),
  // ...
];
```

dan biarkan child:

```dart
// sushitei.r.dart
final sushiteiRoute = <GoRoute>[
  GoRoute(
    path: 'dashboard', // ⬅️ HAPUS slash di depan, biar jadi /sushitei/dashboard
    name: 'sushitei.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => const SushiTeiDashboardUI(),
  ),
];
```

**Catatan penting**:
- Di child, pakai `path: 'dashboard'` (relatif), **bukan** `'/dashboard'`.
- Nama route **wajib unik** di seluruh `GoRouter`.

---

### 🔧 Fix 2 — Kalau sebenarnya cuma mau `/sushitei` aja

Dari redirect:

```dart
final brandPath = '/sushitei';
return brandPath;
```

dan

```dart
return '/sushitei';
```

Keliatan kamu sebenarnya cuma mau 1 path: `/sushitei` untuk dashboard SushiTei.  
Kalau gitu, **hapus saja nested `sushiteiRoute`**, dan pakai satu `GoRoute` ini:

```dart
// brand_routes.dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';
import 'package:stg/brands/sushitei/dashboard/ui/sushitei.d.ui.dart';

final brandRoutes = <RouteBase>[
  GoRoute(
    path: '/sushitei',
    name: 'sushitei.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => const SushiTeiDashboardUI(),
  ),
  GoRoute(
    path: '/hokkaidoya',
    name: 'hokkaidoya.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => Scaffold(appBar: AppBar(title: Text("Hokkaido Ya"))),
  ),
  GoRoute(
    path: '/tomsushi',
    name: 'tomsushi.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => Scaffold(appBar: AppBar(title: Text("Tom Sushi"))),
  ),
  GoRoute(
    path: '/yokayoka',
    name: 'yokayoka.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => Scaffold(appBar: AppBar(title: Text("Yoka Yoka"))),
  ),
  GoRoute(
    path: '/firstfilled',
    name: 'firstfilled.dashboard',
    builder: (context, state) => Scaffold(appBar: AppBar(title: Text("First Filled"))),
  ),
];
```

Dan `sushitei.r.dart` bisa kamu kosongin dulu / dipakai nanti untuk subpage lain (misal `/sushitei/orders`, `/sushitei/settings`, dll).

---

### 🔁 Sesuaikan dengan redirect

Karena sekarang dashboard utamanya di `/sushitei`, redirect-mu sudah pas:

```dart
if (loggedIn && (onLoginPage || onRoot)) {
  if (brand != null) {
    return '/sushitei'; // atau berdasarkan brand (dinamis)
  }
  return '/sushitei'; // fallback
}
```

---

Ringkasnya:

1. **Setiap `name` route harus unik** → jangan ada 2 `'sushitei.dashboard'`.
2. Kalau nested route → child pakai `path: 'dashboard'`, bukan `'/dashboard'`.
3. Kalau cuma perlu `/sushitei` → cukup 1 `GoRoute` di `brandRoutes`, hapus duplikat di `sushiteiRoute`.

Kalau mau nanti bikin banyak sub-halaman di Sushi Tei (orders, profile, dsb), aku bisa bantu bikinin struktur nested route yang rapi juga.

Sip! Kalau di dalam **SushiTeiDashboard** nanti ada **banyak halaman** (cart, notification, history, profile, dsb), berarti kita **harus** pakai **nested routing** yang benar, biar:

- URL tetap hidup → misal:  
  `/sushitei/cart`  
  `/sushitei/notifications`
- Bottom navigation bisa pindah tab tapi **tidak re-render** seluruh dashboard
- Deep linking tetap jalan
- Transition antar fitur **tetap berada di dalam layout utama Sushi Tei Dashboard**

