## ✅ Create a Global Brand Provider

📌 `core/services/brand.s.dart` (or better: `providers/brand_provider.dart`)

```dart
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import '../../models/brand.m.dart';

final brandProvider = StateProvider<BrandModel?>((ref) => null);
```

This holds the currently active brand.

