## Good to check

Ensure your router refresh works:

```dart
refreshListenable: authCoreNotifier,
```

That means when you call:

```dart
ref.read(authCoreProvider).setLoggedIn(true);
```

→ Router auto redirects (`/login` ↔ `/brands`)

