### 🎯 Summary

| Feature | Provider package | Riverpod package |
|--------|-----------------|----------------|
| Access notifier | `Provider.of(context)` | ❌ Not allowed |
| Correct way | `ref.read(...) / ref.watch(...)` | ✅ Yes |
| Reactive updates | `notifyListeners()` | Works with `ChangeNotifierProvider` |

