### 📌 Catatan penting

Jika user **belum login**:

| URL | Redirect |
|-----|----------|
| `/` | → `/login` |
| `/brands` | → `/login` |

Jika **sudah login**:

| URL | Redirect |
|-----|----------|
| `/login` | → `/brands` |
| `/brands/...` | stay |

Jadi aman untuk app dengan auth-based routing.

