## 🔧 Contoh `app_router.dart` (versi rapi & reusable)

```dart
// lib/router/app_router.dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:go_router/go_router.dart';

import '../core/auth/auth_notifier.dart'; // contoh: untuk listen auth state
import 'auth_routes.dart';
import 'brand_routes.dart';

class AppRouter {
  AppRouter._(); // private constructor

  /// Dipanggil di main.dart
  static GoRouter createRouter(AuthNotifier authNotifier) {
    return GoRouter(
      initialLocation: '/login', // atau '/brands' kalau sudah login disimpan
      debugLogDiagnostics: true, // bisa dimatikan di production

      // 🔄 supaya router nge-cek lagi kalau auth berubah
      refreshListenable: authNotifier,

      // 🔒 Redirect logic untuk auth
      redirect: (context, state) {
        final bool loggedIn = authNotifier.isLoggedIn;
        final bool onLoginPage = state.matchedLocation == '/login';

        // Kalau belum login dan bukan di /login → paksa ke /login
        if (!loggedIn && !onLoginPage) {
          return '/login';
        }

        // Kalau sudah login tapi masih di /login → pindah ke /brands
        if (loggedIn && onLoginPage) {
          return '/brands';
        }

        // Tidak ada redirect
        return null;
      },

      // Semua route dikumpulin di sini
      routes: [
        ...authRoutes,   // dari auth_routes.dart
        ...brandRoutes,  // dari brand_routes.dart (yang di dalamnya ada brandA/B/C)
      ],

      // Optional: error page kalau route tidak ketemu
      errorBuilder: (context, state) {
        return Scaffold(
          appBar: AppBar(title: const Text('404')),
          body: Center(
            child: Text('Halaman tidak ditemukan: ${state.error}'),
          ),
        );
      },
    );
  }
}
```

---

## 🧠 Contoh `AuthNotifier` (biar `refreshListenable` jalan)

Kalau kamu belum punya, ini contoh **sederhana**:

```dart
// lib/core/auth/auth_notifier.dart
import 'package:flutter/foundation.dart';

class AuthNotifier extends ChangeNotifier {
  bool _loggedIn = false;

  bool get isLoggedIn => _loggedIn;

  void setLoggedIn(bool value) {
    _loggedIn = value;
    notifyListeners();
  }
}
```

Lalu di `main.dart`:

```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:provider/provider.dart'; // kalau pakai provider
import 'router/app_router.dart';
import 'core/auth/auth_notifier.dart';

void main() {
  runApp(const MyApp());
}

class MyApp extends StatelessWidget {
  const MyApp({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return ChangeNotifierProvider(
      create: (_) => AuthNotifier(),
      child: Builder(
        builder: (context) {
          final authNotifier = Provider.of<AuthNotifier>(context, listen: false);
          final router = AppRouter.createRouter(authNotifier);

          return MaterialApp.router(
            routerConfig: router,
          );
        },
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

