> **Now the “dynamic” behavior:**
> - You want another brand with a different dashboard? Just add new `sections` in `dashboards.json`.
> - Want to change the order? Change the array order.
> - Want different banner texts/heights per brand? Change `title` / `props` in JSON.
> - As long as you use an existing `type` (e.g. `"banner"`, `"promo"`), Flutter will create the widget automatically from the JSON config.

