## 5. Splitting work for 3 developers (with this simpler setup)

### Dev 1 – **App shell + core + auth**

- `main.dart`, `app.dart`
- `src/core/` (models, theme, services, providers, widgets)
- `src/features/auth/` (login page & flow)
- Plug Riverpod + navigation

> Owner of: app startup, login, brand state provider.

---

### Dev 2 – **UI for brand selection + dashboards A/B**

- `features/brand_selection/`
- `features/dashboard/common/`
- `features/dashboard/brand_a/`
- `features/dashboard/brand_b/`

> Owner of: brand switch UI, shared dashboard layout.

---

### Dev 3 – **Dashboards C/D/E + settings**

- `features/dashboard/brand_c/`
- `features/dashboard/brand_d/`
- `features/dashboard/brand_e/`
- `features/settings/`

> Owner of: extra brand layouts, in-app settings, maybe language/theme toggles using extra Riverpod providers.

